{
  "stem": "3360.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When I was in-- at home, I heard-- and this was during the day-- I heard some people walking up the stairs in the-- in the-- stairway, out in the apartment-building stairway.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And these were boots.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You could tell they were boots.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The Nazis all had, with their uniforms, these boots that went up to the knee, those solid, stiff boots.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And you could hear the boots.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then-- we had-- there was the window.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I could see through the window.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there were two-- there was a widow with two young Jewish sons-- I mean, young; they were maybe 20, 22-- living upstairs of us.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And there they had been-- they had been handcuffed and taken into custody.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they were being marched down the stairs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So they had taken these two Jacoby boys.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They passed by our apartment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "How that happened, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Because the name 'Wallach' was a Jewish-- it's a Jewish name.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It's very definitely a Jewish name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And it was listed on the-- at the entrance.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And it's just a mystery.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was just pure luck they did not pick up my father.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I thought, for sure, on the way down, they would stop.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And he wasn't home, of course.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And-- excuse me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I, I took a walk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Whether it was that day-- I, I can't-- I cannot recall which day it was.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I somehow passed by the main synagogue building, which was the synagogue at the Bornstrasse.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And again, that's-- they were all named-- the temple was named after this street it was in.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "The schools were named after the streets that they were on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And the, the synagogue at the Bornstrasse was the main synagogue-- and big, beautiful building.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "B-O-R-N-S-T-R-A-S-S-E, Bornstrasse.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
